column5: So...Looks like i'm going to try my best to squeeze in space for the g2g but just for nov 17 only. and maybe pick up a mustang suit too? Hopefully fishindevil(btw, thanks!!) can help me out a bit with my boat and get her ready by then. Anywhoo.. i couldn't find the g2g page, whos going again? ROLL CALL!  kevin
opps didn't know it was in the hook ups
btw, is everyone launching from the picton habour?  kevin
Some will launch there, maybe even me, and others will launch from Merland Parks private ramp and other spots along the reach.

Hey kevin,im glad i could help you with your boat..  ..anytime bud !!!!! thats what us great OFC'ers are for !!!! im looking forward to seeing you at quinre,and if i can i will go out with you sometime and show you a few walleye tips & tricks to get you started up in your new boat....theres lots of us going,and people will be using different launches,depending on location ,and how bad the wind is blowing ,so dont worry you wont get lost,and i can show you the launches so no worrys bud....cheers
